se\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"an inauspicious start\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"his pommel horse routine\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old Filipino standout started the event at last place after he fell near the end of his pommel horse routine, a mistake that earned him just 11.900 points.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 24-year-old Filipino standout\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"last place\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"his pommel horse routine\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"just 11.900 points\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stayed at the bottom despite getting 13.933 points in still rings.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"13.933 points\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"still rings\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Yulo slowly climbed the standings starting with his stellar showing in vault, where he tied for the third-highest score.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yulo\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"the standings\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"his stellar showing\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"the third-highest score\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He followed it up with a steady execution in parallel bars and horizontal bar, where he posted 13.600 points, before he closed out the rotation in floor exercise.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases